Package org.transitime.api.data.siri Description

For handling SIRI API.

Examples of SIRI feed output can be seen at: http://user47094.vs.easily.co.uk/siri/schema/1.4/examples/index.htm http://user47094.vs.easily.co.uk/siri/schema/1.4/examples/exs_stopMonitoring_response.xml

NYC MTA info can be found at http://bustime.mta.info/wiki/Developers/SIRIVehicleMonitoring http://bustime.mta.info/wiki/Developers/SIRIStopMonitoring http://bustime.mta.info/wiki/Developers/SIRIMonitoredVehicleJourney

UTA has a documented SIRI feed at http://developer.rideuta.com/VehicleByVehcileInstructions.aspx http://developer.rideuta.com/StopMonitoringInstructions.aspx
